# {{context|heraldry|lang=fr}} The [[abyss]] of the shield.

====Usage notes====
* {{fr-note reformed spelling}}
* Often used as if it was a [[pluralia tantum]].
* Unlike the English {{term|abyss|lang=en}}, {{term||abime}} is not the usual term for underwater abysses (the same term, {{term|abysse}}, exists in French), although it is used for them.

